beer.beer_description:
Kronos, it’s always dark and always strong! Not this time, not for GABS and our 5th Birthday year. 

Still very much a strong ale at 9% but layered with “Stout-Esque” if you will raw materials. 

With flaked Barley, Golden Naked Oats, Custom blended coffee beans, vanilla, lactose and cacao give all the flavor notes you could want from our once in a lifetime Kronos offering.

items.checkin_comment: Still having trouble describing this one. But I'm now thinking kind of smooth sweet Belgian golden boozy; with hints of boozy Belgian sweet smoothness. And maybe a dash of coffee/chocolatey hiding deep underneath ...either way, I'll say it again: 9% big ✓
